ull, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020965, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "There is no god save Allah, the glorious, the supreme. There is no god save Allah, the mighty, the oft-returning. There is no god save Allah, the one, the dominating. There is no god save Allah, the single who has no associate, the only God, we surrender ourselves to His will. There is no god save Allah, the single who has no associate, the only God, we are those who are sincere. There is no god save Allah, the single who has no associate, the only God, we are those who worship you. There is no god save Allah, Muhammad is the messenger of Allah, Ali is the vicegerent of Allah. Blessings of Allah be on His best creation, the manifestation of His pleasure, Muhammad and his excellent & purified children, on account of Your mercy, O most merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HUL JALEE-LUL JABAA-RO. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HUL A’ZEE-ZUL GHAF-FAARO. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HUL WAAHE-DUL QA-HAARO. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HO WAH-DAHU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU, ELAA-HAN WAAHE-DAN WA NAHNO LAHU MUSLE-MOONA. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HO WAH-DAHU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU ELAA-HAN WAAHE-DAN WA NAHNO LAHU MUKH-LESOON. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HO WAH-DAHU LAA SHAREE-KA LAHU ELAA-HAN WAAHE-DAN WA NAHNO LAHU A’ABE-DOONA. LAA ILAAHA ILLAL LAA-HO MOHAMMA-DUR RASOO-LUL LAAHE A’LIYYUN WALIY-UL-LAAHE, WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA KHAIRE KHALQE-HI WA MAZ-HARE LUTFE-HI MOHAMMADIN WA AALE-HI AJMA-E’E-NAT TAYYE-BEE-NAT TAAHE-REENA BE-RAH-MATE-KA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEEN.", "ArabicText1": "لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ الْجَلِيْلُ الْجَبَّارُ۔ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ الْعَزِيْزُ الْغَفَّارُ۔  لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ الْوَاحِدُ الْقَهَّارُ۔  لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَهٗ لَا شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ، اِلٰهًا وَاحِدًا وَنَحْنُ لَهٗ مُسْلِمُوْنَ۔ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَهٗ لَا شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ، اِلٰهًا وَاحِدًا وَنَحْنُ لَهٗ مُخْلِصُنْ۔ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَهٗ لَا شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ، اِلٰهًا وَاحِدًا وَ نَحْنُ لَهٗ عَابِدُوْنَ۔ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ مُحَمَّدٌ رَّسُوْلُ اللهِ عَلِيٌّ وَلِيُّ اللهِ، وَ صَلَّي اللهُ عَلٰي خَيْرِ خَلْقِهٖ وَمَظْهَرِ لُطْفِهٖ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاٰلِهٖ اَجْمَعِيْنَ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ بِرَحْمَتِكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8